about: High-Quality USB C to HDMI Cable】 - Made of strong nylon material, this USB C to HDMI Cable is anti-fraying and anti-tearing. With the durable connector and aluminum housing, it ensures high-speed data transmission without interference and performs better at heat dissipation. The premium-quality USB-C connector ensures a tight connection and stable signal transmission, and the non-slip design allows you to plug and unplug easily. 【4K 60Hz Visual Feast】: You can have up to 4K@60Hz revolution with this hdmi cable.Backward compatible with 1080P, 1080I and 720P. This way, you can enjoy your favorite TV shows on a bigger screen. (*Note: If you want to mirror your phone screen, please turn off Dex mode manually) 【Wide applicability】It is compatible with laptops and Android smartphones equipped with USB C ports supporting DisplayPort Alternate Mode.Compatible with M1/M2 devices, iPhone15,iPhone 15 Plus,iPhone 15 Pro,iPhone 15 Pro Max,MacBook Pro2016-2023,MacBook Air2018-2022,iMac2017-2021, Mac Mini2018-2023,iPad Pro2018-2022,iPad Air2020-2022,Surface Book 2/3,Surface Go/Go 2, Surface Laptop Go,Surface Laptop 3,Surface Pro 7/X,Chromebook,Dell XPS 17/15/13,Galaxy S22/S21/S20,Note 20/10/9,Tab S9/S8,LG V40/V35/V30/V20 and more.
